        a(href='//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/2.5') CC BY-NC 2.5&#x20;
        | license.

    br

    small Check out the source code for this website on&#x20;
        a(href='//github.com/shreyasminocha/xkcd-viewer') Github
        | .
